metadata.name: Kerala- God's own country
metadata.description:
Kerala is a state in India and also known as God's own country. In May, 2022 I went on a trip to Kerala with my friends and while exploring the backwaters of Kerala, I saw this abandoned boat and clicked this. It is my one of the favorite shot from that trip.

Artist: Himanshu Pagariya  
Supply: Unlimited  
Duration: 2 weeks
